*"Glas* se čuo preko celog grada. (A voice was heard throughout the city.)

*"Glas* njegovog sina je dopirao do njega iz drugog kraja sobe. (The voice of his son was reaching him from the other end of the room.)

*Čulo se *glas*no vrištanje. (A loud scream was heard.)

*Ona je vikala *glas*no da se čuje. (She was shouting loudly to be heard.)

*Iznenada je stalo *glas*anje. (Suddenly the noise stopped.)